      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed using mean absolute relative error (MARE), root mean square error (RMSE), and U95 uncertainty intervals. NIH MARE = 8.3%; pressure rise RMSE = 4.2%. Validation uncertainty (Uval) computed per ASME V&V 20 methodology. Achieved level exceeds requirement due to rigorous uncertainty decomposition."
