      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal blood pump — the same device class and geometry family as the CPB device under assessment. Operating conditions (2000–3500 RPM, 2–8 L/min) encompass the five COU operating points. Blood analog (40% glycerol in water) rheology matches in vitro hemolysis test conditions per ASTM F1841."
