      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis damage model selection justified with reference to published validation evidence for comparable flows.",
      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on published validation for confined rotating flows in blood pumps (Bludszuweit 1995; Fraser et al. 2011). Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power law model selected; limitations acknowledged for high-shear transient exposures. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±15% NIH based on published model comparison studies."
    },
    {
