      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond what is captured under Test Conditions is not required at MRL 2. FDA benchmark dataset uses standardized blood analog per ASTM F1841; sample-to-sample variability addressed in experimental uncertainty. Scoped out per assessment plan."
